## Description {#details}

A private class template which derives from <code><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/aaresults/concept">Concept</a></code> and wraps some other type.

This models the concept by directly forwarding each interface point to the wrapped type which must implement a compatible interface. This provides a type erased binding.
